Package: stamp
Type: Package
Title: Disk I/O with Content Hashing for R Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9016
Authors@R: person("R.Andres", "Castaneda",
    email = "acastanedaa@worldbank.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1154-1374"))
Description: Lightweight tools to read from and write to disk with atomic
    I/O, sidecar metadata, stable content/code hashing, and a minimal
    versions catalog. Prefer 'qs2' format with graceful fallback to 'qs'.
